✅ Common Standard IPTV Categories

Category
Description
News
News channels (international, regional, political)
Sports
All sports-related channels
Movies
Channels focusing on films and blockbusters
Entertainment
General TV content, series, variety shows
Music
Music videos, concerts, music channels
Kids
Children’s content, cartoons, and educational shows
Documentary
Educational and factual programs (e.g., Nat Geo, History)
Religious
Religious or spiritual programming
Lifestyle
Cooking, fashion, travel, home improvement
Radio
Audio-only stations (FM/AM simulcasts or online radio)
Educational
Learning, language, school-related channels
Comedy
Comedy-focused content (can overlap with Entertainment)
Adult
18+ channels (usually filtered or password-protected)
Local
Local/regional terrestrial TV stations
International
Foreign-language channels not tied to local audience
Variety
Mixed-genre channels (can be fallback if unclear where it fits)





